'''2015年莫三比克啤酒中毒事件'''，是指2015年1月9日在[[莫三比克|莫三比克]]發生的集體食物中毒案，事件造成75人死亡，230人不適。事發地點位於該國[[太特省|太特省]]{{link-en|卡布拉·巴薩區|Cahora-Bassa District}}的齊迪馬（Chitima）的一場葬禮。與會者因飲用飲用受[[唐菖蒲伯克氏菌|唐菖蒲伯克氏菌]]（''Burkholderia gladioli''）汙染的私釀{{tsl|en|Millet beer|小米啤酒|}}（pombe）而中毒<ref name="CID" />。

事件發生時，官方將中毒原因歸因到啤酒內摻混[[鱷魚|鱷魚]]的膽汁<ref name="RT">{{cite news|title='Crocodile poison' beer kills nearly 70 at funeral in Mozambique|url=http://rt.com/news/221623-poisonous-beer-kills-56/|accessdate=2015-01-12|agency=[[路透社|Reuters]]|website=[[RT电视台|rt.com]]|date=2015-01-12|archive-date=2015-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150112234315/http://rt.com/news/221623-poisonous-beer-kills-56/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》雜誌的文章否定了這種假設，並認為[[毛地黄属|毛地黄]]類的有毒植物才是中毒的主因<ref name="Camillo">{{cite news|last1=Camillo|first1=Emmanuel|title=At Least 52 Dead After Drinking Poisoned Beer In Mozambique|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/01/11/mozambique-poison-beer_n_6450996.html|accessdate=2015-01-12|agency=Associated Press|website=[[赫芬顿邮报|The Huffington Post]]|date=2015-01-12|archive-date=2015-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150113181442/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/01/11/mozambique-poison-beer_n_6450996.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="TG">{{cite news|title=At least 69 die after drinking contaminated beer at Mozambique funeral|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/jan/12/contaminated-beer-at-funeral-kills-56-in-mozambique|accessdate=2015-01-12|agency=[[美联社|Associated Press]]|newspaper=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|date=2015-01-12|archive-date=2015-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150113050826/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/jan/12/contaminated-beer-at-funeral-kills-56-in-mozambique|dead-url=no}}</ref>。直到當年11月才確認中毒的原因是細菌汙染造成的食品中毒<ref name="allafrica.com">{{cite news |title=Mozambique: Mass Poisoning Caused By Bacterial Contamination |url=http://allafrica.com/stories/201511050128.html |website={{tsl|en|allafrica.com||allafrica.com}} |date=2015-11-04 |accessdate=2016-02-07 |archive-date=2016-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160207152138/http://allafrica.com/stories/201511050128.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 事件經過 ==
[[File:COLLECTIE_TROPENMUSEUM_Man_drinkt_bier_(pombe)_op_het_bordes_van_Dr._Thoden_van_Velzen_terwijl_kinderen_toekijken_TMnr_20014576_(cropped).jpg|左]]
据莫桑比克电台报道，该国西部[[太特省|太特省]]的齐迪马和桑噶村（Songa）1月9日举行的一場葬礼過后，有69人死亡，196人送院治疗。中毒者當時皆饮用了自制的酵母啤酒，一种用谷物和膛发酵的饮料。小米啤酒是莫桑比克的传统发酵饮料，由高粱、麸皮、玉米、糖和{{Le|粟酒裂殖酵母|Schizosaccharomyces pombe}}（''Schizosaccharomyces pombe''）釀製而成，跟欧洲传统的酿酒酵母不同<ref name="forbes2" />。

事件翌日首位被报告的死者，是饮料攤的老板及其两个亲戚和四位邻居。卡布拉·巴萨地区的健康、社区行动和妇女总管宝拉·贝尔纳多（Paula Bernardo）表示，当地医院都患有绞痛和腹泻的病人挤爆，许多人已经死去<ref name="forbes2" />。截至2015年1月12日，共有169人仍在医院接受治疗，这一数字在13日下降至35人<ref name="abc2">Death Toll Rises to 72 From Contaminated Beer in Mozambique, MAPUTO, Mozambique, January 13, 2015, By EMMANUEL CAMILLO [http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/death-toll-rises-72-contaminated-beer-mozambique-28186224 Associated Press] {{Wayback|url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/death-toll-rises-72-contaminated-beer-mozambique-28186224 |date=20150120224942 }}</ref>。[[莫桑比克总统|莫桑比克总统]][[阿曼多·格布扎|阿曼多·格布扎]]宣布全国哀悼三天<ref name="NBC2" />。

== 调查 ==
早期报告认为啤酒含有的“鳄鱼胆”是中毒的因素，当地从业者在销售时称之为“nduru”<ref>{{cite journal|title=Crocodile bile, a poison: myth or reality?|first1=N. Z.|authorlink=Norman Nyazema|date=June 1984|journal=Central African Journal of Medicine|issue=6|volume=30|pages=102–103|issn=0008-9176|pmid=6478501|last1=Nyazema}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Crocodile (Crocodylus niloticus) bile acids and arrow poisons|first1=N. Z.|date=June 1985|journal=Central African Journal of Medicine|issue=6|volume=31|pages=114–116|issn=0008-9176|pmid=4042148|last1=Nyazema}}</ref>。《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》杂志发表的在线文章引述相关研究，表明鳄鱼胆相对无害<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Nyazema |first1=N. Z. |authorlink=Norman Nyazema |title=Crocodile bile, a poison: myth or reality?|journal=Central African Journal of Medicine|date=June 1984|volume=30|issue=6|pages=102-103|pmid=6478501|accessdate=2015-01-13|issn=0008-9176}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Nyazema|first1=N. Z.|title=Crocodile (Crocodylus niloticus) bile acids and arrow poisons|journal=Central African Journal of Medicine|date=June 1985| volume=31|issue=6 |pages=114-116|pmid=4042148 |accessdate=2015-01-13|issn=0008-9176}}</ref>，认为导致中毒的有效成分，很可能是一些[[强心苷|强心苷]]，如[[地高辛|洋地黄]]。[[洋地黄|洋地黄]]是毛地黄花的品种、地高辛的正常来源，被欧洲殖民者引进后，在该地区极为常见<ref name="forbes">{{cite journal|title=Did Crocodile Bile In Beer Really Kill 69 People In Mozambique?|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/davidkroll/2015/01/12/what-is-crocodile-bile-and-is-it-really-poisonous/|last=Kroll|first=David|date=2015-01-12|journal=Forbes|accessdate=2015-01-13|archive-date=2015-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150418205422/http://www.forbes.com/sites/davidkroll/2015/01/12/what-is-crocodile-bile-and-is-it-really-poisonous/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。毛地黄原产于非洲，学名Ceratotheca triloba，类似于有毒植物，但不含地高辛<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.herbs-treatandtaste.blogspot.com/2012/07/south-african-foxglove-false-foxglove.html | title = South African Foxglove - A False Foxglove: Health Benefits and Potential Uses of the South African Foxglove | author = Abbas | date = 2012-07-02 | accessdate = 2015-01-17 | archive-date = 2015-01-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150114232626/http://herbs-treatandtaste.blogspot.com/2012/07/south-african-foxglove-false-foxglove.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在《福布斯》文章中，大卫·克罗尔写道，所有对鳄鱼胆的提及，在初次报告后被删掉<ref name="forbes">{{cite journal |title=Did Crocodile Bile In Beer Really Kill 69 People In Mozambique? |first=David |last=Kroll |date=2015-01-12 |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/davidkroll/2015/01/12/what-is-crocodile-bile-and-is-it-really-poisonous/ |journal=Forbes |accessdate=2015-01-13}}</ref>。

在鼓内发现的啤酒、血液和可疑物样品，被送去国家重点实验室分析<ref name=RT /><ref name=NBC>{{cite news|title=Bad Beer Kills At Least 69 People, Hospitalizes 169 in Mozambique|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/bad-beer-kills-least-69-people-hospitalizes-169-mozambique-n284441|accessdate=2015-01-12|publisher=[[NBC新聞|NBC News]]|date=2015-01-12|agency=Reuters|archive-date=2015-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150115093117/http://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/bad-beer-kills-least-69-people-hospitalizes-169-mozambique-n284441|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，警方发言人Zeferino Sande表示，警方尚未找到线索，用来酿造啤酒的木桶已失踪<ref name="abc">Death Toll Rises to 72 From Contaminated Beer in Mozambique,
MAPUTO, Mozambique, Jan 13, 2015, By EMMANUEL CAMILLO
[http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/death-toll-rises-72-contaminated-beer-mozambique-28186224 Associated Press] {{Wayback|url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/death-toll-rises-72-contaminated-beer-mozambique-28186224 |date=20150120224942 }}</ref>。

